```{r}
library(tidyverse)
```

```{r}
data = data.table(table)

set.seed(999)
a = sample(data, 30) %>%
  na.omit()

check_factorstructure(a)

dataparallel <- fa.parallel(a, cor = "poly", fa = "pc")
dataparallel$pc.values
dataparallel$pc.sim



res1 = fa(a, 4, cor = 'poly', rotate = 'geominQ', fm = 'wls')
res1

res = fa(a, 5, cor = 'poly', rotate = 'geominQ', fm = 'wls')
res

res = fa(a, 6, cor = 'poly', rotate = 'geominQ', fm = 'wls')
res2
```
